 1997-18901997-12-170AGRI-FOOD,  ,  ,  , 
PrecisRegulations Amending the FISH INSPECTION REGULATIONS which will require that importers of canned and ready-to-eat fish products maintain records of the processes used to produce them, ban the importation of puffer fish of the family Tetraodontidae, create an importer licensing system, ensure that fees are shared equitably between licenced fish importers and require that the actual shrimp content of shrimp cocktail be clearly marked on the label of this product.
